# Enforce LF line endings in the working tree on every machine.
# Without this, core.autocrlf=true checks files out as CRLF, but `npm link`
# rewrites the bin shebang line to LF, leaving lib/cli.js with mixed endings
# that git reports as modified. Pinning LF keeps checkout and npm link in sync.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binaries must never be line-ending normalized.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.wasm binary
